text: Jacek Daniluk (1 September 1961 - 6 September 1986) was a Polish equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1980 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1961 births Category:1986 deaths Category:Polish male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Poland Category:Equestrians at the 1980 Summer Olympics Category:People from Kwidzyn
